title: Week 1 materials
textContent:
This is everything I will be starting pre production with, many of it has been worked on in the past slowly and has comprised the building blocks for this monster of a film.

I am using Toon Boom Harmony for production as well as post production.

I am skilled at effects animation and staging, 

in this project I will be trying to master character animation, as well as background animation. Some lip sync will be implemented but is not a focus
